data.description: Come see this  Ranch style home in a quiet cul-de-sac.  3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom on the main floor.  With an additional 2 non-conforming bedrooms and 1 bath and open family room on the lower level.  There is also plenty of room for storage with the storage room.  Property does not require flood insurance.
